data.name: Label10.Text
data.value: - have had most types of cancer - have heart conditions - have received blood, platelets, plasma or any other blood products after 1 January 1980 - have had an organ transplant - have tested positive for HIV - are a hepatitis B or C carrier - have injected non-prescribed drugs including body-building and injectable tanning agents. You may be able to donate if a doctor prescribed the drugs
